Habitats.Beyond Toril:
* In the [[Abyss]], abyssal pine trees that looked diseased and twisted grew in the Deathroot Woods of [[Hollow's Heart]].{{Cite dragon/357/Demonomicon of Iggwilv: Demogorgon: Prince of Demons|36}}
* In the [[Outer Planes]], pine trees were known to grow in the [[plane]]s of [[Jotunheim]] and the [[Beastlands (plane)|Beastlands]]. 
* Pines could be found growing within forests on the [[demiplane]] of [[Barovia]].
